title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 2 2022

description:
New York to raise covid "alert" level, amid rising violent crime. Fauci maskless at pre-Correspondent's Dinner cocktail party, but wouldn't go to WHCD. Bill Maher gets it about Twitter and free speech. Biden economic disaster taking down stock market. CNN analyst: We're heading to gates of hell because Elon Musk bought Twitter. Tune in to The Buck Sexton Show podcast for history specials. Liberals search for meaning in climate religion.
